title: Beartooth - Disgusting [Japanese Edition] (2015)
description:
Beartooth are an American metalcore band from Columbus, Ohio. They are signed to Red Bull Records and managed by The Artery Foundation since 2013 along with Caleb Shomo's electronic act, Class. Their debut EP Sick was released on July 26, 2013, followed by their debut full-length album Disgusting on June 10, 2014.
